Overview
LeLoop (LearningLoop), a social media platform that is intended to leverage AI to convert text-heavy, dry academic materials (books, articles, research papers) into engaging, bite sized motion graphic short videos. It functions like an educational counterpart to TikTok,
complete with a personalized discovery feed, creator uploads, and social features (likes,comments, shares).

The Problem
University students often experience stress, burnout, and lack of motivation when dealing with long academic materials. Many students turn to highly addictive short video platforms such asTikTok or Instagram as a way to escape stress. While these platforms provide entertainment, they also consume valuable time that could have been used productively.

  Why LeLoop?
LeLoop addresses this issue by transforming academic learning into an engaging and visually interactive experience. Instead of forcing students to choose between entertainment and studying, the platform combines both experiences into one environment. LeLoop replaces 
addictive, unproductive screen time with a verified, highly engaging educational alternative.
  
  
